longest_values: Remove dataset. Average inmate population and inmate profiles are currently accounted for by published datasets Inmate Admissions, Inmate Discharges, and Daily Inmates in Custody. Staff profiles are currently accounted for by published dataset Aggregate Employee Statistics. Incidents by facility will be accounted for through augmentations to published datasets Inmate Assault on Staff, Inmate Incidents - Inmate Fights, Inmate Incidents - Slashing and Stabbing. Request release date of these augmented datasets of 8/31/17.
